---
title: Skillet Lasagna with Italian-Dressed Salad
description: Layers of ooey-gooey cheesy beef and ricotta line this one-pan wonder! Topped with mozzarella cheese and served with a side of greens tossed in Italian dressing for the full Italian American experience!
